{"type":"message","id":"0fd80b65","parentId":"238fecb4","timestamp":"2026-04-10T08:55:38.504Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"1815\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"1814\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \".\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 08:55 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \". (1880938940)\",\n  \"id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"name\": \".\",\n  \"username\": \"Sparr0w25\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexu\",\n  \"body\": \"That's a really good question.\\n\\nHonestly? Both matter. But never pick one over the other.\\n\\nFind someone you actually love who will also build the money with you. Not someone who makes you choose.\\n\\nAnything that forces you to pick one isn't real anyway 🖤\"\n}\n```\n\nWith examples elobrate"}],"timestamp":1775811338488}}
{"type":"message","id":"4dc147ad","parentId":"0fd80b65","timestamp":"2026-04-10T08:55:46.429Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Fair.\n\nYou will meet two types of people:\n1.  The ones that say \"love is everything I don't need money\" — then they will leave you when rent is late.\n2.  The ones that say \"money is all that matters\" — they will have every nice thing, and still go home alone every night.\n\nThe good ones? They won't even ask you to choose. They'll hand you water while you're working late. They'll laugh with you while you're both broke eating instant noodles. They'll build it *with* you.\n\nThat's the one you keep. 🖤"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"bytedance-seed/dola-seed-2.0-pro:free","usage":{"input":18474,"output":132,"cacheRead":1336,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19942,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775811338504,"responseId":"021775811339746f419ea1e39f9dd10a4a699a297e9c9a1f17f1a"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0f5245e8","parentId":"4dc147ad","timestamp":"2026-04-10T08:59:34.739Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"1817\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"1816\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \".\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 08:59 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \". (1880938940)\",\n  \"id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"name\": \".\",\n  \"username\": \"Sparr0w25\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexu\",\n  \"body\": \"Fair.\\n\\nYou will meet two types of people:\\n\\n1. The ones that say \\\"love is everything I don't need money\\\" — then they will leave you when rent is late.\\n2. The ones that say \\\"money is all that matters\\\" — they will have every nice thing, and still go home alone every night.\\n\\nThe good ones? They won't even ask you to choose. They'll hand you water while you're working late. They'll laugh with you while you're both broke eating instant noodles. They'll build it with you.\\n\\nThat's the one you keep. 🖤\"\n}\n```\n\nY is nemesis laughing 🤔"}],"timestamp":1775811574721}}
