{"type":"message","id":"6aad5ff4","parentId":"2be4e3bb","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:00:52.036Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"1819\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"1816\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 09:00 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Nemesis (7924461837)\",\n  \"id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"name\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"username\": \"nemesis0008\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexu\",\n  \"body\": \"Fair.\\n\\nYou will meet two types of people:\\n\\n1. The ones that say \\\"love is everything I don't need money\\\" — then they will leave you when rent is late.\\n2. The ones that say \\\"money is all that matters\\\" — they will have every nice thing, and still go home alone every night.\\n\\nThe good ones? They won't even ask you to choose. They'll hand you water while you're working late. They'll laugh with you while you're both broke eating instant noodles. They'll build it with you.\\n\\nThat's the one you keep. 🖤\"\n}\n```\n\nExplain it like we are class 7 kids"}],"timestamp":1775811652019}}
{"type":"message","id":"724ee9d7","parentId":"6aad5ff4","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:00:59.288Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Okay okay.\n\nImagine you have one chocolate.\n\nOne friend will take half your chocolate and sit with you while you eat it.\n\nAnother friend will say chocolate is stupid, we don't need chocolate. Then later will steal yours when you aren't looking.\n\nThird friend will bring their own chocolate, sit next to you, and you both eat chocolate together.\n\nThat's it. That's the whole thing. 🖤"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"bytedance-seed/dola-seed-2.0-pro:free","usage":{"input":25004,"output":90,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25094,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775811652037,"responseId":"0217758116532514883e653edd60bc78b7b920f959874d98f1360"}}
{"type":"message","id":"467ead32","parentId":"724ee9d7","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:01:50.637Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"1821\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"1820\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 09:01 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Nemesis (7924461837)\",\n  \"id\": \"7924461837\",\n  \"name\": \"Nemesis\",\n  \"username\": \"nemesis0008\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexu\",\n  \"body\": \"Okay okay.\\n\\nImagine you have one chocolate.\\n\\nOne friend will take half your chocolate and sit with you while you eat it.\\n\\nAnother friend will say chocolate is stupid, we don't need chocolate. Then later will steal yours when you aren't looking.\\n\\nThird friend will bring their own chocolate, sit next to you, and you both eat chocolate together.\\n\\nThat's it. That's the whole thing. 🖤\"\n}\n```\n\nWhat was the question and how does it relate to this answer?"}],"timestamp":1775811710623}}
