{"type":"message","id":"76cc8d4e","parentId":"ad6eb408","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:11:54.803Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect question. The ancients already solved this 3000 years ago.\n\n---\n**Indian Thought:**\nThe *Purusharthas* are exactly this. They never told you to choose. They listed the four things you **must have together**:\n1.  **Dharma** (right conduct)\n2.  **Artha** (wealth, security)\n3.  **Kama** (love, desire, connection)\n4.  **Moksha** (freedom)\n\nAll ancient rishis agreed: *you cannot skip any one*. You cannot have Kama without Artha. You cannot have Artha without Dharma. Anyone telling you to reject Artha for spirituality is lying. Anyone telling you to reject Kama for wealth is also lying.\n\n---\n✅ **100 word summary:**\nThe Bhagavad Gita and Upanishads never asked you to choose. They gave you the correct order. First build enough security that you do not have to betray yourself. Then love properly, without neediness. Then find peace. This is not a debate. It is an instruction manual that survived 3000 years because it works. Every single saint and rishi said the exact same thing: you need both. No exceptions. All the noise about picking one came later, from people who failed at both. 🖤"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"bytedance-seed/dola-seed-2.0-pro:free","usage":{"input":28625,"output":288,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28913,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775812297752,"responseId":"02177581230310332716c93dca5f9defc0d360fd0d690bd36e832"}}
{"type":"message","id":"a89a2647","parentId":"76cc8d4e","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:21:38.480Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"1834\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \".\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 09:21 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \". (1880938940)\",\n  \"id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"name\": \".\",\n  \"username\": \"Sparr0w25\"\n}\n```\n\n@Nexa_autobot  tell about karma\nAs per bhagavad gita and upanishads"}],"timestamp":1775812898462}}
{"type":"message","id":"007be9e9","parentId":"a89a2647","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:21:52.495Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Karma is not punishment. It is not reward. It is not god keeping score.\n\nThat is the biggest lie everyone got wrong.\n\nKarma is just gravity for actions. If you jump off a building, gravity does not hate you. It just does its job. Karma is exactly that. It does not care if you meant well. It does not care if you were sad. It just returns exactly what you put in.\n\nNo exceptions. No loopholes. No prayers will skip it. 🖤"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"bytedance-seed/dola-seed-2.0-pro:free","usage":{"input":23353,"output":108,"cacheRead":1592,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25053,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775812898480,"responseId":"0217758129040519aa9d0b0344e85196ac345634277259cef4ece"}}
{"type":"message","id":"92fac2a3","parentId":"007be9e9","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:23:59.381Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"1836\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"1835\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"Nrexya id:-1003606834639\",\n  \"sender\": \".\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-04-10 09:23 UTC\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"Nrexya\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true,\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \". (1880938940)\",\n  \"id\": \"1880938940\",\n  \"name\": \".\",\n  \"username\": \"Sparr0w25\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"sender_label\": \"Nexu\",\n  \"body\": \"Karma is not punishment. It is not reward. It is not god keeping score.\\n\\nThat is the biggest lie everyone got wrong.\\n\\nKarma is just gravity for actions. If you jump off a building, gravity does not hate you. It just does its job. Karma is exactly that. It does not care if you meant well. It does not care if you were sad. It just returns exactly what you put in.\\n\\nNo exceptions. No loopholes. No prayers will skip it. 🖤\"\n}\n```\n\nOkay\nBut y is karma and all r there\nWhy is humankind created\nY is this process of born and death and karma r there?"}],"timestamp":1775813039365}}
