{"type":"message","id":"02963d37","parentId":"9ad7937a","timestamp":"2026-04-10T09:24:24.847Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Nobody knows the actual why.\n\nBut the Gita gives the only honest answer that ever made sense:\n\nIt is not a test. It is not a lesson. It is not a game.\n\nIt is just play.\n\nBrahman got bored. So it split itself into every single thing that ever existed, forgot it was all the same thing, and is just running around playing all the parts. Fighting, loving, suffering, winning. All of it. Just for the experience.\n\nYou are not here to learn anything. You are here to forget you already know everything, so you can feel it. 🖤"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"bytedance-seed/dola-seed-2.0-pro:free","usage":{"input":23876,"output":130,"cacheRead":1592,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25598,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775813056709,"responseId":"021775813057911ec39001cad8ae999c8f17eed1b37944e33aee7"}}
